text: Scooby-Doo! and the Goblin King is a 2008 movie. == Heroes == This is a list about the heroes who appear in the movie. * Scooby-Doo - a large, brown dog. He is voiced by Frank Welker (the voice of Fred). * Shaggy - a very lazy slacker who has a green V-neck shirt. He says "Like, Zoinks!". He's best friends with Scooby-Doo. He is voiced by Casey Kasem. * Fred - leader of the gang. He is voiced by Frank Welker (the voice of Scooby). * Velma - She's very smart. She wears glasses. She is voiced by Mindy Cohn. * Daphne - Fred's crush. She's really beautiful. She is voiced by Grey DeLisle. ==Other websites== Category:Scooby-Doo movies Category:2008 animated movies Category:Direct-to-video movies Category:Halloween movies Category:Warner Bros. direct-to-video movies
